opify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_Snapins.ai_487974244_18058369541511779_3962561349722037191_n_1080.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gglV0yKrbqN_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"gglV0yKrbqN_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/image16.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZHuYgoc8x_text","label":"ggZHuYgoc8x_text","default":"1. One Use = A Noticeable Difference"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvDN5djePx_text","label":"ggvDN5djePx_text","default":"<p>We’ve tried the serums, The toners and The creams that “might” work in 90 days. With this mask? The change is almost immediate. Most women report firmer texture, a visibly smoother surface, and a rested, radiant appearance—without wondering if it’s just better lighting. It works quickly enough that it doesn’t feel like another beauty gamble.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_Snapins.ai_468093164_17921313579005496_5027706299210191973_n_1080.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_tablet_src","label":"ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_tablet_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_8ae32f92f34f5de3366bb345087b722f.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_Snapins.ai_468093164_17921313579005496_5027706299210191973_n_1080.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNzvrSfCrV_text","label":"ggNzvrSfCrV_text","default":"2. It’s Perfect for Tired Skin (and Tired Schedules)"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxwUzin72S_text","label":"ggxwUzin72S_text","default":"<p>Let’s face it: most of us don’t have time for 8-step skincare routines. That’s what makes this mask so easy to love. You can wear it while making dinner, folding laundry, working remotely, or catching up on your favorite shows. It starts off jelly-like and slowly dries clear, so you can forget it’s even there. Some even sleep in it. One step, effortless glow.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj-_y-Y_PO_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggj-_y-Y_PO_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Results_1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj-_y-Y_PO_srcSet_tablet_src","label":"ggj-_y-Y_PO_srcSet_tablet_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_Snapins.ai_461930601_900003792007461_5276257373326152319_n_1080.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj-_y-Y_PO_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggj-_y-Y_PO_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Results_1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjPk9bJpvM_text","label":"ggjPk9bJpvM_text","default":"3. It Was Formulated for Skin That’s Lived"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUrpHf4v9e_text","label":"ggUrpHf4v9e_text","default":"<p>This isn’t a one-size-fits-all product. It’s formulated with real life in mind—sun exposure, hormone changes, stress, sleepless nights. Hydrolyzed marine collagen helps restore elasticity, while niacinamide and peptides calm the skin and reduce dullness. It’s made for mature skin, and it respects your skin’s history, instead of pretending it never happened.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggA3rMFyw6n_text","label":"ggA3rMFyw6n_text","default":"Your skin reset starts now - just like theirs"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZHs5tgyVn_text","label":"ggZHs5tgyVn_text","default":"<p>Here's what real women say about the mask that fits their lifestyle:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGeGfcLZi7_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggGeGfcLZi7_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/image16.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfqRyY20qQ_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggfqRyY20qQ_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/star_3.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gglDSkVvmUq_text","label":"gglDSkVvmUq_text","default":"<p>I was hesitant to try something new at 53, but this mask didn't irritate my sensitive skin at all. It softened my laugh lines and gave me a healthy glow the next morning.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>— MARIA T., 53</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaHivsSBRW_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggaHivsSBRW_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/image8.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggyVGSwUo3T_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggyVGSwUo3T_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/star_3.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNxmGbB3EU_text","label":"ggNxmGbB3EU_text","default":"<p>\"After juggling work and family, I barely had time for self-care. This mask made it easy. Just once a week and my skin feels hydrated and vital again.\"</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>— JANELLE R., 41</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjrmijUVzb_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggjrmijUVzb_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/image3.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-882vwGfS_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg-882vwGfS_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/star_3.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gguBFMUhrqM_text","label":"gguBFMUhrqM_text","default":"<p>\"I am postmenopausal and my skin was getting dry and dull. This mask brought back a glow that I haven't seen in years. Even my daughter noticed!\"</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>— DIANE L., 59</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsVwikOkoU_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggsVwikOkoU_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/image1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj1aPId-3r_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggj1aPId-3r_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/star_3.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGTOwbK4iC_text","label":"ggGTOwbK4iC_text","default":"<p>\"The mask makes me feel good even when I'm not wearing makeup. It's my go-to product for events or long work days. I wish I had discovered it sooner.\"</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>— RACHEL M., 47</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDA-nvWEHj_label","label":"ggDA-nvWEHj_label","default":"<p>Shop Now</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_Snapins.ai_461930601_900003792007461_5276257373326152319_n_1080.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_tablet_src","label":"gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_tablet_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_509ad04972d74c387b664586b9438c82.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"gghzDPqYWS2_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_Snapins.ai_461930601_900003792007461_5276257373326152319_n_1080.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQPtwZzMvG_text","label":"ggQPtwZzMvG_text","default":"4. Minimal Products. Maximum Payoff."},{"type":"html","id":"ggxpEEAWkOo_text","label":"ggxpEEAWkOo_text","default":"<p>You know that drawer full of half-used products? Most women find themselves reaching for this mask again and again—and shelving everything else. It simplifies your routine without compromising results. It tightens, hydrates, smooths, and soothes all at once, which means fewer products, fewer steps, and better skin.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/36347b4da9104eff674ad4eb69feeb60.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_tablet_src","label":"ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_tablet_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_21c31ebc929e-hailey-bieber-pink-face-mask_jpg.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/36347b4da9104eff674ad4eb69feeb60.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHIzq54zz__text","label":"ggHIzq54zz__text","default":"5. It’s Like a Facial, Without the Facialist"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQ78Sg6Zrx_text","label":"ggQ78Sg6Zrx_text","default":"<p>We all love that post-facial feeling—but not the price or scheduling. This mask delivers similar results: skin that looks refreshed, dewy, and balanced. The kind of glow that usually takes a professional touch. But instead of $150 and a trip to the spa, you can do it from your own couch (wine optional).</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYy6grbLeA_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggYy6grbLeA_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/2d545aa53feb9e741e0c7e0fce361f8b.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYy6grbLeA_srcSet_tablet_src","label":"ggYy6grbLeA_srcSet_tablet_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_4a84c883593649e49ddda6c20c3fe3ee_tplv-omjb5zjo8w-resize-jpeg_800_800.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYy6grbLeA_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggYy6grbLeA_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/2d545aa53feb9e741e0c7e0fce361f8b.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOkzpODfF8_text","label":"ggOkzpODfF8_text","default":"6. Skin-Loving, Clean Ingredients You Can Trust"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3BajX3jAe_text","label":"gg3BajX3jAe_text","default":"<p>There’s a lot of noise in skincare. This formula cuts through it. With clean, cruelty-free ingredients and no harsh chemicals, it’s designed for even the most sensitive skin. No stinging, no weird fragrance, and no overcomplication. Just good, effective skincare that respects your skin barrier.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggl71u75c7R_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggl71u75c7R_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Bio_Collagen_Main_Photo_2_22b3adc2-0470-49e4-9bff-94ea2a6c1c17.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggl71u75c7R_srcSet_tablet_src","label":"ggl71u75c7R_srcSet_tablet_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_Snapins.ai_447778010_431048143184490_4824332307233201183_n_1080.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggl71u75c7R_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggl71u75c7R_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Bio_Collagen_Main_Photo_2_22b3adc2-0470-49e4-9bff-94ea2a6c1c17.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTCZJLSmNN_text","label":"ggTCZJLSmNN_text","default":"7. It’s Selling Out for a Reason"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOGc25WEdF_text","label":"ggOGc25WEdF_text","default":"<p>It’s not hype. It’s word of mouth. Women who try it don’t just like it—they repurchase it. They tell their daughters, best friends, sisters. They start using it weekly and notice their skin bounce back, glow more, and require less fuss. The fact that it sells out often isn’t a marketing trick. It’s a result of how well it works.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggFYCvYdkkz_text","label":"ggFYCvYdkkz_text","default":"Ready to finally give your skin the care it truly deserves? 💕"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7UbdrEDNi_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg7UbdrEDNi_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_8ae32f92f34f5de3366bb345087b722f.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7UbdrEDNi_srcSet_tablet_src","label":"gg7UbdrEDNi_srcSet_tablet_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_Snapins.ai_468093164_17921313579005496_5027706299210191973_n_1080.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7UbdrEDNi_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"gg7UbdrEDNi_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_8ae32f92f34f5de3366bb345087b722f.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggL99cbnlZo_text","label":"ggL99cbnlZo_text","default":"<p><strong>GUARANTEED:</strong> In just a few hours, the Nifora face mask can make your skin glow in ways you haven’t seen in years.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>If you’ve ever thought that only pricey serums or high-end facials could deliver results — think again. One use, and you’ll understand why so many women in their 40s, 50s, and 60s say their skin feels calmer, smoother, and more lifted.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2Qn3hJVgP_text","label":"gg2Qn3hJVgP_text","default":"<p>Clinically proven results — even while you sleep</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggw6GWQLv30_text","label":"ggw6GWQLv30_text","default":"<p>1–2 uses a week is all it takes to see real difference</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8qbjp2nD2_text","label":"gg8qbjp2nD2_text","default":"<p>Gentle and safe for sensitive, mature skin</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5jhvAeOg-_text","label":"gg5jhvAeOg-_text","default":"<p>Try it for 60 days, completely risk-free</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7_objrOEc_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg7_objrOEc_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/banner.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUMmUh3HgV_label","label":"ggUMmUh3HgV_label","default":"<p>Shop Now</p>"}],
